  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Female or male patients at least 18 years of age

          -  Patients who are at serious risk of hypertrophic scarring (due to family history,
             race, recent surgery, etc)

          -  Able and willing to provide informed consent and likely to complete all study visits

          -  All Fitzpatrick skin types will be evaluated

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Known contraindications to Dermatix or any of its components

          -  Age of scar is &gt; 4 months

          -  Keloid scars (scars with increased fibroblastic activity that has exceeded the
             boundaries of the original scar)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
